This holiday was so boring, didnt go search went for job(Anyway i also don't like to work) haha. That is the reason why i have only been wasting my time this holiday!! Althought the time now is 12.20am, but i am still so not sleepy. Guess i have past my sleeping hours, sigh=( ..

This is the first time i play snooker untill no money sigh, How will you feel when your parents just do everything behind your back? Sigh let don't talk about it. erm by the way anyone know why i keep getting this kind of weird feeling?Write in the comment and tell me can?  plz >< I really need HELP!!.
